Gate (Erc20 DAI Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard DAI "Dai")
Gate (Erc20 REP Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard REP "Augur")
Gate (Erc20 USDC Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard USDC "USD Coin" 6)

-- Now deploy our cTokens
Gate (CToken cZRX Address) (CToken Deploy CErc20 cZRX "Test 0x ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 ZRX Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (CToken cBAT Address) (CToken Deploy CErc20 cBAT "Test Basic Attention Token ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 BAT Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (CToken cDAI Address) (CToken Deploy CErc20 cDAI "Test Dai ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 DAI Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (CToken cREP Address) (CToken Deploy CErc20 cREP "Test Augur ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 REP Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (CToken cETH Address) (CToken Deploy CEther cETH "Test Ether ðŸ“ˆ" (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (CToken cUSDC Address) (CToken Deploy CErc20 cUSDC "Test USD Coin ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 USDC Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 2e-4 8)

